> **What this document is.** The statement a reviewer (and every customer
> security questionnaire) asks for: how long subscriber data lives in the
> solution, **what happens to it when the package is uninstalled or the contract
> ends**, where it resides, how backups interplay with deletion, and whether
> deletion is automatic or request-based. The deletion-on-uninstall row is the
> one reviewers most often probe — answer it concretely or it bounces.

